--------------------------------steps--------------------------------------


1.install LAMP
2.install kafka
3.run the zookeeper by the command given in kafka.txt file.
4.run the kafka server
5.create topic for both input and output stream given in kafka.txt
6.run the wordCount program by the command given in kafka.txt
7.in order to run the php file paste them inside the /var/www/html folder
8.run the "run1.sh" file by typing watch -n 10 <path to run1.sh file>
9.run the consumer command from kafka.txt
10. Open the index.php file in web browser
11. submit data of your choice.
12. View result in consumer cli. 

